metadata.Summary: This frame shows the OpenAI Operator interface interacting with n8n. On the left, Operator provides chat messages guiding the user to navigate back to the n8n canvas, while the right panel displays the n8n 'Executions' view for the 'Handling Job Application Submissions' workflow. A 'Save changes before leaving?' modal is open in n8n, and the AI Assistant panel on the right continues to display troubleshooting guidance for the 'Upload File to Record' node error.
